title: The 2018 Toyota Sequoia gets some much-needed attention - Roadshow
text:
1 of 23 The 2018 Toyota Sequoia gets some much-needed attention 
On the aging Sequoia, the addition of the TRD Sport version is a small shot in the arm for a model that hasn't had a complete make over since 2008. Photo by: Andrew Krok/Roadshow Pricing is currently unavailable. 
The Sequoia TRD Sport can be had as a 4x2 and 4x4 with power coming from a 5.7-liter V8,
